column5: Ok, it has been a while since I posted anything so I messed up the first time
Nice meeting you out there on the weekend! My team finished 3rd place with 16lbs+ in a small derby that day. All the best this weekend!
Well done man !!!! Wow those buckets have been hanging out at the all you can eat buffet table that's for sure !!!!! Lol .... Excellent catch !!! Tight-lines.
Nice fish, fat little piggies for sure!
Chris, those are fat pigs for sure!
Those are incredible largemouth!  Guess they are from Simcoe, what an amazing fishery.
Those are incredible largemouth!  Guess they are from Simcoe, what an amazing fishery. Not Simcoe. Quinte
Some solid largos Chris.  Nicely done.
wow what a size thanks for sharing.
